.SH NAME
citadel-whatsapp-down - Stop the WhatsApp bridge (auth state is preserved)


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcitadel whatsapp down [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Stop the WhatsApp bridge (auth state is preserved)


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for down


.SH OPTIONS INHERITED FROM PARENT COMMANDS
\fB--debug\fP[=false]
	Enable debug output

.PP
\fB--no-color\fP[=false]
	Disable colorized output


.SH SEE ALSO
\fBcitadel-whatsapp(1)\fP
